OL,3,CAssaults on Translink almost hit 400
OL,5,FOn Trains, buses and the glider.
OL,6,FAssaults have become common place on
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's public transport
OL,8,Fnetwork.
OL,10,FBetween 2019 and 2024 there were 392
OL,11,Fassaults on Translink workers, which
OL,12,Fis roughly one every five days.
OL,14,FOne worker is calling on those
OL,15,Fcarrying out the attacks to ask
OL,16,Fthemselves, what if it was a member of
OL,17,Ftheir family or themselves, as attacks
OL,18,Frise.
