OL,3,CAssaults on Translink almost hit 400
OL,5,FSince 2019 there have been 113
OL,6,Fassaults on staff on trains, 178 on
OL,7,Fbuses and 101 on glider services.
OL,9,FMervyn Adair has been working on the
OL,10,FGlider for six years. He is a Customer
OL,11,Fand Revenue Protection Officer, who
OL,12,Fhas experienced this violence first
OL,13,Fhand....
OL,15,F"I was poutting two people off who did
OL,16,Fnot have valid tickets to travel. They
OL,17,Fbecame verbally abusive, so I put on
OL,18,Fthe camera, they then became violent
OL,19,Fand attacked me and my colleague.
OL,20,FMervyn said.
