OL,5,FHe added: " I got punched in the face
OL,6,Fand got a suspected broken nose and
OL,7,Fmild concussion and I had to attend
OL,8,Fhospital.
OL,10,F"My colleague who was with me, got
OL,11,Fkicked in the leg and had to get
OL,12,Fmedical treatment to his leg."
OL,14,FMervyn also urged those who carry out
OL,15,Fattacks to think about who they are
OL,16,Fattacking.
OL,18,F"They have to remember they have
OL,19,Ffamily members, we all have people at
OL,20,Fhome, wives, children, mothers,
OL,21,Ffathers all out there doing a job.
